  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t习近平访问沙特和阿拉伯国家们出的一个联合公告里面说要和平解決大通布、小通布和阿布穆萨三岛问题，结果把伊朗人得罪了，气得伊朗外交部都用中文发推了。中共本来想两头吃发表一下中立客观的声明和稀泥，结果还是踩到了伊朗的底线，现在伊朗网友们开始支持台湾独立了，真是笑死我了🤣。<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYTNiODc0ODEzOGJhYTEzMDM0MjQwLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a3b8748138baa13034240.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a3b8748138baa13034240.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a3b8748138baa13034240.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYWFlM2JmYmI5MjZiYzBmNmRmYTAxLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/aae3bfbb926bc0f6dfa01.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/aae3bfbb926bc0f6dfa01.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/aae3bfbb926bc0f6dfa01.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cudGhlbmV3c2xlbnMuY29tL2FydGljbGUvMTc3OTkx\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.thenewslens.com/article/177991\">https://www.thenewslens.com/article/177991</a> </div>",
